snippet.title: FATE: Reawakened Console Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
FATE is coming to consoles for the very first time!

That's right, FATE: Reawakened will be available on PlayStation 4, PlayStation 5, Xbox Series X|S, and Nintendo Switch. 

Whether you grew up with FATE or are discovering it for the first time, this is your chance to experience the epic journey on your preferred platform!
